  <title>Introduction</title>

  <p><app>Videos</app>, also known as <app>Totem</app>, is an application for
  playing media; it can play video. You can use it to watch
  movies or stream media from the Internet.</p>

  <note style="advanced">
    <p><app>Videos</app> is based on <gui>GStreamer</gui>, a plugin-based
    multimedia framework. Thanks to <gui>GStreamer</gui>, <app>Videos</app>
    has superior extensibility and supports a larger variety of media
    formats.</p>
  </note>

